        <span class="text">Show</span> cost breakdown
      </a>
      <ul class="show-hide" id="treatment-cost">
        <li class="lh"><strong>$1,000 per fistula repair surgery</strong></li>
        <li>40%: Treatment</li>
        <li>30%: Accommodations &amp; food</li>
        <li>20%: Patient transportation &amp; outreach</li>
        <li>10%: Medicines &amp; vitamins</li>
      </ul>
