  <div class="row">
        <div class="small-3 columns treatment_badge">
      <img class="badge burns" src="/wp-content/themes/samahope-underscore/images/icon-burns@2x.png" width="120" height="120">
    </div>
    <div class="small-9 columns treatment_description">
      <h3>Burn Repair Focus</h3>
      <p>
        Without immediate access to acute burn care, burn 
        injuries begin to heal themselves by tightening and pulling skin 
        together to form scar tissue (contractures) while attaching to another 
        body part. These contractures greatly inhibit function and movement, and 
        can cause severe disabilities. Post-burn reconstructive surgery releases 
        these contractures to restore previous mobility, function, and appearance.
      </p>
      <a href="#" class="show-toggle" rel="treatment-cost">
